OL,9,G1445 The Americas
OL,10,     F9/11. This episode focuses on the
OL,11,     Fbehaviour of animals living on and
OL,12,     Fclose to the West Coast, including
OL,13,     Fsea wolves, giant Pacific
OL,14,     Foctopuses, sea otters, salamanders
OL,15,     Fand blue whales.
OL,16,G1530 The Americas
OL,17,     F10/11. This episode features the
OL,18,     Fbehaviour of animals living in and
OL,19,     Fnear Patagonia, including
OL,20,     Frockhopper penguins, pumas,
OL,21,     FChilean stag beetles, Darwin's
OL,22,     Frheas, orcas and elephant seals.
